dct_description_sm: Township map of Cranford including Kenilworth and Garwood sections and portions of the Central Railroad of New Jersey and the Garden State Parkway. Legend indicates locations of municipal buildings, schools and churches. Map was prepared by the League of Women Voters of Cranford, March 1966.
dct_creator_sm: League of Women Voters of Cranford
